Amazon Customer
5.0 out of 5 stars Cute and comfortable!
Reviewed in the United States on October 24, 2021
Very comfortable boots! I purchased them for a Halloween costume with the hope that I could wear them with my jeans, etc. afterwards. They fit the bill! They definitely look like vinyl, but I'm okay with that. They have a strip of silver beading chain around the foot bed (which I didn't notice in the Amazon pic), which is cute. As you can see in the pic, though, the bead chain is not installed perfectly on one of the boots (there's another spot on the other side of the boot). I'm wondering how long this cute added touch will last on the boot...
